{
  "video_id": "UM1ZAFcu1Vc",
  "title": "Fake news v fact: The battle for truth | The Economist",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 2680.0,
      "end_time": 5300.0,
      "text": "Modern technology is helping the state"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 5300.0,
      "end_time": 6720.0,
      "text": "watch its citizens."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 6720.0,
      "end_time": 9870.0,
      "text": "But that same technology it also letting citizens"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 9870.0,
      "end_time": 11430.0,
      "text": "watch the state."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 11430.0,
      "end_time": 13240.0,
      "text": "We know that Facebook is spying on us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 13240.0,
      "end_time": 14970.0,
      "text": "we know that Google is spying on us."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 14970.0,
      "end_time": 18220.0,
      "text": "But those mediums can also become mediums"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 18220.0,
      "end_time": 19610.0,
      "text": "of counter forensics."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 19610.0,
      "end_time": 21280.0,
      "text": "We are watching the watchers."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 21280.0,
      "end_time": 23953.0,
      "text": "We are reversing the forensic gaze."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 31772.0,
      "end_time": 33290.0,
      "text": "The rise of social media"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 33290.0,
      "end_time": 35430.0,
      "text": "and the proliferation of smart phones"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 35430.0,
      "end_time": 38763.0,
      "text": "has made it easier than ever for people to consume news."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 39670.0,
      "end_time": 41713.0,
      "text": "But not all this information is true."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 42580.0,
      "end_time": 44760.0,
      "text": "Some governments use these platforms"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 44760.0,
      "end_time": 48522.0,
      "text": "to disseminate propaganda, and monitor citizens behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 49660.0,
      "end_time": 53400.0,
      "text": "Now this technology has also helped to turn the tables"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53400.0,
      "end_time": 53933.0,
      "text": "on the powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57920.0,
      "end_time": 60810.0,
      "text": "Every comment, every photo, every video,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 60810.0,
      "end_time": 63340.0,
      "text": "is a clue to ultimately getting at the truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 63340.0,
      "end_time": 64980.0,
      "text": "The big challenge is to figure out how"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 64980.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67600.0,
      "text": "we find all those clues and ultimately use them"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 67600.0,
      "end_time": 69333.0,
      "text": "almost like pieces in a puzzle."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70440.0,
      "end_time": 72560.0,
      "text": "Alexa Koenig is a law professor"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 72560.0,
      "end_time": 74350.0,
      "text": "and investigator."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 74350.0,
      "end_time": 77410.0,
      "text": "She gathers evidence from multiple digital sources,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 77410.0,
      "end_time": 80320.0,
      "text": "to investigate some of the biggest human rights abuses"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 80320.0,
      "end_time": 82279.0,
      "text": "in the 21st century."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 82280.0,
      "end_time": 85110.0,
      "text": "So many war crime cases fall apart at fairly early"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 85110.0,
      "end_time": 86580.0,
      "text": "stages of prosecution."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 86580.0,
      "end_time": 88840.0,
      "text": "One of the big challenges is that prosecutors"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 88840.0,
      "end_time": 91110.0,
      "text": "are over-relying on witness testimony."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 91110.0,
      "end_time": 92929.0,
      "text": "And of course with time and trauma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 92930.0,
      "end_time": 94563.0,
      "text": "a testimony becomes fallible."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 98800.0,
      "end_time": 100450.0,
      "text": "Miss Koenig&#39;s team has helped investigate"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 100450.0,
      "end_time": 103233.0,
      "text": "atrocities in Myanmar, Syria and Yemen."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 104150.0,
      "end_time": 106340.0,
      "text": "Unlike traditional investigators,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 106340.0,
      "end_time": 108493.0,
      "text": "her team uses open source evidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 109660.0,
      "end_time": 112900.0,
      "text": "So we brought together people doing big data analytics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 112900.0,
      "end_time": 115700.0,
      "text": "satellite imagery, remote sensing, people who were"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 115700.0,
      "end_time": 117410.0,
      "text": "thinking through how cellphones could be harnessed"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 117410.0,
      "end_time": 119913.0,
      "text": "and support the stories of survivors."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 121780.0,
      "end_time": 123850.0,
      "text": "The team has investigated atrocities"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 123850.0,
      "end_time": 125762.0,
      "text": "in Myanmar in 2017."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 127210.0,
      "end_time": 130700.0,
      "text": "The evidence proved that the army had used Facebook&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 130699.99999999999,
      "end_time": 133500.0,
      "text": "wide reach in the country to post false information"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 133500.0,
      "end_time": 137343.0,
      "text": "inciting hatred against the Rohingya Muslim minority."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 139100.0,
      "end_time": 141640.0,
      "text": "This type of evidence is gaining traction"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 141640.0,
      "end_time": 145290.0,
      "text": "and is being used by the international criminal courts."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 145290.0,
      "end_time": 147769.0,
      "text": "Open source information that you can find online"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 147770.0,
      "end_time": 150730.0,
      "text": "is increasingly being used by groups like the United Nations"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 150730.0,
      "end_time": 152760.0,
      "text": "and by the International Criminal Court."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 152760.0,
      "end_time": 155530.0,
      "text": "It released its first ever arrest warrant based on"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 155530.0,
      "end_time": 158263.0,
      "text": "information pulled from social media in Libya."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 163800.0,
      "end_time": 165100.0,
      "text": "Meanwhile, Bellingcat, a group"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 165100.0,
      "end_time": 168380.0,
      "text": "of open source experts, has been investigating the poisoning"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 168380.0,
      "end_time": 171120.0,
      "text": "of a former Russian spy, Sergei Skripal"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 171120.0,
      "end_time": 173270.0,
      "text": "and his daughter in 2018."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 173270.0,
      "end_time": 175803.0,
      "text": "They have made some striking discoveries."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 177300.0,
      "end_time": 180340.0,
      "text": "Bellingcat disclosed the names of three Russian agents"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 180340.0,
      "end_time": 182730.0,
      "text": "who they allege were involved in the attack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 182730.0,
      "end_time": 185380.0,
      "text": "strengthening the suspicion that it was sanctioned"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 185380.0,
      "end_time": 186713.0,
      "text": "by the Russian State."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 187800.0,
      "end_time": 190700.0,
      "text": "In response, the Russian authorities claimed that"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 190700.0,
      "end_time": 193649.0,
      "text": "the men were tourists, but Bellingcat proved that"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 193650.0,
      "end_time": 196650.0,
      "text": "the three men were high ranking members of the Russian army."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 197500.0,
      "end_time": 199840.0,
      "text": "One of the agents had even been honored"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 199840.0,
      "end_time": 202400.0,
      "text": "by President Vladimir Putin personally."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 202400.0,
      "end_time": 205250.0,
      "text": "What Bellingcat did was they began to comb social media"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 205250.0,
      "end_time": 207810.0,
      "text": "and find the profiles of the people"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 207810.0,
      "end_time": 209750.0,
      "text": "who were thought to have been involved,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 209750.0,
      "end_time": 211810.0,
      "text": "that Russia was saying were just tourists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 211810.0,
      "end_time": 214420.0,
      "text": "and ultimately establish the true identities"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 214420.0,
      "end_time": 216950.0,
      "text": "in a way that really shocked the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 216950.0,
      "end_time": 219329.0,
      "text": "Bellingcat cross referenced photo and video"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 219330.0,
      "end_time": 222270.0,
      "text": "evidence released by the British and Russian authorities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 222270.0,
      "end_time": 226290.0,
      "text": "with social media to find the men&#39;s true identities."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 226290.0,
      "end_time": 228880.0,
      "text": "This is not the first time the state has been accused"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 228880.0,
      "end_time": 230662.0,
      "text": "of trying to cover its tracks."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 239910.0,
      "end_time": 243880.0,
      "text": "Governments are trying to release false information"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 243880.0,
      "end_time": 246300.0,
      "text": "about things that have taken place."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 246300.0,
      "end_time": 249420.0,
      "text": "We need to not only establish what has taken place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 249420.0,
      "end_time": 252869.0,
      "text": "but to deconstruct government statements"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 252870.0,
      "end_time": 254223.0,
      "text": "that are misleading."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 255700.0,
      "end_time": 258440.0,
      "text": "Eyal Weizman is an open source expert"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 258440.0,
      "end_time": 260500.0,
      "text": "based in the UK."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 260500.0,
      "end_time": 263310.0,
      "text": "The most recent incident which he has investigated"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 263310.0,
      "end_time": 265940.0,
      "text": "raises questions about the death of Palestinians"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 265940.0,
      "end_time": 267703.0,
      "text": "during an Israeli airstrike."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 274500.0,
      "end_time": 278200.0,
      "text": "In 2018, these two boys were sitting on a roof top."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 278200.0,
      "end_time": 281300.0,
      "text": "They were killed moments after taking this selfie."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 283740.0,
      "end_time": 286700.0,
      "text": "The Israeli armed forces said they fired"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 286700.0,
      "end_time": 289332.0,
      "text": "non-lethal warning shots to clear the area of civilians."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 291200.0,
      "end_time": 293663.0,
      "text": "They call this tactic &#39;nocking on the roof."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 294710.0,
      "end_time": 297820.0,
      "text": "Hours later, the Israeli army released a video"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 297820.0,
      "end_time": 300210.0,
      "text": "which appears to show four warning shots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 300210.0,
      "end_time": 301893.0,
      "text": "followed by the main strike."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 304200.0,
      "end_time": 307450.0,
      "text": "But forensic architecture stitched together mobile phone"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 307450.0,
      "end_time": 311170.0,
      "text": "and CCTV footage disputing their claim."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 311170.0,
      "end_time": 314130.0,
      "text": "They allege the Israeli army did not release a video"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 314130.0,
      "end_time": 316730.0,
      "text": "of the first shots which killed the boys."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 316730.0,
      "end_time": 319170.0,
      "text": "Instead, it substituted it with a video"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 319170.0,
      "end_time": 321283.0,
      "text": "of the third strike from another angle."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 322150.0,
      "end_time": 324349.0,
      "text": "The Israeli army denied distorting evidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 330150.0,
      "end_time": 333250.0,
      "text": "Investigating state operations isn&#39;t cheap."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 333250.0,
      "end_time": 335760.0,
      "text": "It takes time and resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 335760.0,
      "end_time": 338930.0,
      "text": "One big question is always where&#39;s the money coming from"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 338930.0,
      "end_time": 340200.0,
      "text": "to do this kind of work."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 340200.0,
      "end_time": 342370.0,
      "text": "There are some individual donors who really believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 342370.0,
      "end_time": 344680.0,
      "text": "in the power of technology for social good."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 344680.0,
      "end_time": 346880.0,
      "text": "And increasingly we still do see some states that are"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 346880.0,
      "end_time": 348909.0,
      "text": "really interested in the power and possibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 348910.0,
      "end_time": 351390.0,
      "text": "of pulling together information."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 351390.0,
      "end_time": 353219.0,
      "text": "The evidence and practices of groups"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 353220.0,
      "end_time": 355680.0,
      "text": "such as Bellingcat and forensic architecture"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 355680.0,
      "end_time": 357683.0,
      "text": "are open to everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 357683.0,
      "end_time": 361240.0,
      "text": "This evidence is traceable and verifiable."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 361240.0,
      "end_time": 363563.0,
      "text": "But law makers must approach it with caution."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 364400.0,
      "end_time": 367200.0,
      "text": "The use of this evidence in court is in its infancy"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 367200.0,
      "end_time": 369349.0,
      "text": "and raises several problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 369350.0,
      "end_time": 372470.0,
      "text": "I think so few judges today are trained in ways to really"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 372470.0,
      "end_time": 375920.0,
      "text": "interrogate what makes for a good digital investigation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 375920.0,
      "end_time": 377820.0,
      "text": "that there&#39;s really a two-fold risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 377820.0,
      "end_time": 380980.0,
      "text": "The first risk is that they&#39;re going to look at this very"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 380980.0,
      "end_time": 384580.0,
      "text": "slick sexy package and they&#39;re gonna find it so convincing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 384580.0,
      "end_time": 386219.0,
      "text": "that they ultimately don&#39;t interrogate"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 386220.0,
      "end_time": 387770.0,
      "text": "the underlying bits of information."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 387770.0,
      "end_time": 390359.0,
      "text": "The second risk, of course, is that they&#39;re just going"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 390360.0,
      "end_time": 392866.0,
      "text": "to look at this and say I have no way to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 392866.0,
      "end_time": 395320.0,
      "text": "the original sources of this information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 395320.0,
      "end_time": 397730.0,
      "text": "and so they dismiss it out of hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 398756.0,
      "end_time": 400000.0,
      "text": "It is increasingly difficult"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 400000.0,
      "end_time": 402300.0,
      "text": "to separate fact from fiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 402300.0,
      "end_time": 406000.0,
      "text": "But crowd source investigations offer a new way."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 406000.0,
      "end_time": 407580.0,
      "text": "Giving a voice to victims"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 407580.0,
      "end_time": 409582.0,
      "text": "and holding the powerful to account."
    }
  ]
}